552
00:28:14,620 --> 00:28:16,900
I can’t remember
those who are unremarkable.

553
00:28:21,860 --> 00:28:23,140
Your Grace, you are from a noble family.

554
00:28:23,460 --> 00:28:24,740
Why do you pick on Xiaoru?

555
00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:27,820
Anle, you know what?

556
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:31,060
These crab-eating tools
are quite useful.

557
00:28:32,420 --> 00:28:34,020
Count Cheng’an is thoughtful.

558
00:28:34,100 --> 00:28:35,980
