The crab’s shell is thin and crisp.

560
00:28:41,500 --> 00:28:42,540
It’s better to peel it by hand.

561
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:43,860
I don’t need the crab-eating tools.

562
00:28:45,060 --> 00:28:46,300
If I remember it correctly,

563
00:28:46,940 --> 00:28:47,820
these crabs

564
