Childish.

574
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:19,380
<i>Xie’s Mansion</i>

575
00:29:19,380 --> 00:29:20,620
<i>Xie’s Mansion</i>
I’ll punish Xie Qilin hard

576
00:29:21,140 --> 00:29:22,300
