opposite to the dream.

634
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:10,220
Mother, my dream of
the broken engagement came true.

635
00:32:10,820 --> 00:32:12,660
If he really becomes blind,

636
00:32:12,900 --> 00:32:14,380
then we...

637
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:17,260
Don’t be afraid.

638
00:32:17,580 --> 00:32:18,700
Except for His Majesty,

639
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:19,860
