640
00:32:19,900 --> 00:32:20,860
Exactly.

641
00:32:20,980 --> 00:32:22,380
We still got your grandmother.

642
00:32:22,620 --> 00:32:24,300
Even if His Majesty
doesn’t care about me,

643
00:32:24,300 --> 00:32:25,980
he’ll still show some respect
to the Princess Royal.

644
00:32:26,060 --> 00:32:26,660
Don’t be afraid.

645
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:27,940
Hua.

646
00:32:28,300 --> 00:32:30,140
Why can’t they understand?

647
00:32:30,140 --> 00:32:31,860
If you want to forget someone...

648
00:32:31,860 --> 00:32:33,380
Am I thinking too much about it?

649
00:32:33,620 --> 00:32:35,180
Then you have to find a new one.

650
00:32:37,420 --> 00:32:38,220
Forget it.

651
00:32:38,300 --> 00:32:39,340
-Hua!
-Baroness!

652
00:32:39,620 --> 00:32:40,900
You haven’t had the cubilose!

653
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:41,740
There are still a lot of it!

654
00:32:42,580 --> 00:32:43,700
Go ahead.

655
00:32:46,820 --> 00:32:51,220
Long live Your Majesty!

656
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:53,620
<i>Emperor Yunqing</i>

657
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:55,220
<i>Emperor Yunqing</i>
You may rise.

658
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:01,900
In the meeting today, I want to...

