00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,620
Minister Xie.

660
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:10,660
What’s wrong with your forehead?

661
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:18,100
Your Majesty, death cannot
atone for my offense!

662
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:19,900
What offense?

663
00:33:19,900 --> 00:33:21,020
I’m incompetent.

664
00:33:21,340 --> 00:33:22,460
I failed to protect

665
00:33:22,820 --> 00:33:26,380
