666
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:30,300
It’s outrageous!

667
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:32,060
Who stole the plaque?

668
00:33:32,260 --> 00:33:33,220
No one stole it!

669
00:33:34,020 --> 00:33:35,420
It was smashed!

670
00:33:36,460 --> 00:33:37,420
Really?

671
00:33:39,140 --> 00:33:39,980
It was really smashed?

672
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:42,020
Who is so bold?

673
00:33:43,300 --> 00:33:44,460
Your Majesty, please take a look.

674
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:47,580
I remember I didn’t smash the plaque.

675
00:33:48,740 --> 00:33:50,020
Who did it?

676
00:33:50,580 --> 00:33:53,300
Ban Huai and his son,
and a bunch of bandits!

677
00:33:54,060 --> 00:33:55,740
<i>Royal Family</i>

678
00:33:55,740 --> 00:33:57,660
Ban Huai, what happened?

679
00:34:00,620 --> 00:34:01,500
Your Majesty.

680
00:34:02,220 --> 00:34:04,300
His son broke off
the engagement with Hua.

681
00:34:05,020 --> 00:34:07,500
He eloped with a brothel woman.

682
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:11,620
Hua was furious and ran away.

683
00:34:11,900 --> 00:34:13,940
We were worried
that she would go to Xie’s Mansion

684
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:15,180
and make mistakes.

685
00:34:15,460 --> 00:34:18,180
So I took someone to visit Count Xie.

686
00:34:19,300 --> 00:34:21,860
But Count Xie stayed
behind closed doors.

687
00:34:23,300 --> 00:34:26,180
Your Majesty, it was my fault.

688
00:34:26,700 --> 00:34:27,740
If you want to blame anyone,

689
00:34:29,020 --> 00:34:30,100
just blame Count Xie.

690
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:32,140
You...! Your Majesty!

691
00:34:32,220 --> 00:34:33,580
All right.

692
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:34,220
Your Majesty.

693
00:34:35,820 --> 00:34:39,100
Count Cheng’an, you always act fair.

694
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:41,380
What do you think about this?

695
00:34:44,460 --> 00:34:45,220
Your Majesty.

696
00:34:45,900 --> 00:34:48,740
If I remember it correctly,

697
00:34:49,260 --> 00:34:50,700
it was the Xie family
who proposed the marriage,

698
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:53,780
and now the Xie family
unilaterally broke it off.

699
00:34:55,220 --> 00:34:56,860
They not only broke their words,

700
00:34:57,180 --> 00:34:58,580
but also hurt Baroness Ban’s reputation.

701
00:34:59,380 --> 00:35:00,460
In the final analysis,

702
00:35:00,780 --> 00:35:02,300
the Xie family is indeed unrighteous.

703
00:35:02,820 --> 00:35:04,420
It’s understandable
that Marquis Jingting and his son

704
00:35:04,420 --> 00:35:05,620
got furious about it.

705
00:35:07,260 --> 00:35:09,580
Your Majesty, Count Cheng’an is right!

706
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:12,180
But... But he broke

707
00:35:12,180 --> 00:35:13,860
the plaque you gave me in person!

708
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:14,740
All right.

709
00:35:15,100 --> 00:35:17,980
I’ve got the answer.

710
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:25,100
You arranged someone
to keep watch on the Ban family,

711
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:26,220
and something odd happened.

712
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:28,300
His Majesty didn’t
punish the Ban family.

713
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:30,580
Instead, he sent
a carriage of playthings

714
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:31,500
to Marquis Jingting’s Mansion.

715
00:35:33,060 --> 00:35:35,900
Looks like the Princess Royal
is behind this.

716
00:35:36,780 --> 00:35:37,860
I didn’t expect His Majesty

717
00:35:38,370 --> 00:35:39,340
<i>Wang Qu, Brainman in the Rongs</i>
to still have scruples

718
00:35:39,340 --> 00:35:40,340
<i>Wang Qu, Brainman in the Rongs</i>
about the Princess Royal.

719
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:41,980
If it wasn’t for the Princess Royal

720
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:43,860
and her husband General Ban

721
00:35:44,180 --> 00:35:45,180
assisting His Majesty all the way,

722
00:35:46,420 --> 00:35:47,740
I’m afraid Daye

723
00:35:48,060 --> 00:35:49,540
would have been taken away by others.

724
00:35:49,620 --> 00:35:50,220
Young Master!

725
00:35:52,460 --> 00:35:52,940
Young Master.

726
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,260
Go ahead. What did you find?

727
00:35:57,180 --> 00:35:58,100
After my public
and private investigation,

728
00:35:58,420 --> 00:35:59,220
I finally found one

