734
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:15,660
Young Master, do you think

735
00:36:16,340 --> 00:36:17,740
His Majesty has anything to do with it?

736
00:36:19,500 --> 00:36:20,540
If so,

737
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:22,940
I’m afraid Tiger Tally
can’t get away with

738
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:25,260
what happened back then.

739
00:36:26,300 --> 00:36:28,180
Here is the imperial decree!

740
00:36:32,740 --> 00:36:35,100
Xie Qilin, the son of Xie Chengyan,

741
00:36:35,180 --> 00:36:37,700
is lascivious.

742
00:36:37,980 --> 00:36:39,500
He broke the royal covenant

743
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:42,300
and committed an unforgivable sin.

744
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:45,460
With immediate effect,
he is dismissed as a senior licentiate.

745
00:36:46,060 --> 00:36:48,740
He is not allowed to take the test.
Respect this.

746
00:36:50,820 --> 00:36:51,540
Receive the decree.

747
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:54,260
Thank you, Your Majesty.

748
00:36:56,180 --> 00:37:02,700
<i>Royal Family</i>

