in the east of the city.

769
00:38:17,620 --> 00:38:19,100
Why don’t you go to taste the tea?

770
00:38:19,100 --> 00:38:20,380
Yeah, you should go.

771
00:38:20,380 --> 00:38:22,700
I don’t have the mood.

772
00:38:23,820 --> 00:38:24,460
Hua.

773
00:38:25,300 --> 00:38:28,180
Mother gave me the task.

774
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:30,940
