795
00:39:17,460 --> 00:39:18,220
Let’s go.

796
00:39:18,780 --> 00:39:20,260
Go, go, go.

797
00:39:20,340 --> 00:39:21,100
Let’s go.

798
00:39:29,060 --> 00:39:31,860
