800
00:39:36,900 --> 00:39:39,540
Look at this clear sky.

801
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:42,460
The cloudless blue sky
with white clouds.

802
00:39:42,460 --> 00:39:43,820
I’m going back if you keep nagging.

803
00:39:45,620 --> 00:39:46,220
I’ll shut up.

804
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:54,900
<i>Rong’s Mansion</i>

805
00:39:55,820 --> 00:39:56,660
Rong’s Mansion?

806
00:39:58,100 --> 00:39:59,940
We are not going to the tea house.

807
00:40:00,900 --> 00:40:02,540
How dare you lie to me?

808
00:40:02,540 --> 00:40:03,500
No, no, no.

809
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:05,420
Hua.

810
00:40:05,740 --> 00:40:08,420
A few days ago, Count Cheng’an

